lish form, <i>Wealdhere</i>. It was a very popular name in medieval England, normally pronounced ‘Water’."],"variants":[{"name":"Walther","meanings":["from <i>wald</i> ‘rule’ + <i>heri</i> ‘army’; name of the famous medieval minnesinger  Walther von der Vogelweide  (  <i>c.</i>1170– <i>c.</i>1230 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Walter Bamfield was born about 1440, in Poltimore, Devon, England, United Kingdom, his father, William Bamfield, was 36 and his mother, Margaret Pauncefoote, was 17. He had at least 1 son with Grace Pudsey. He died on 1 September 1478, at the age of 39."},"et":{"about 1440–01 Sep 1478":"umbes 1440–1. september 1478","1440–1478":"1440–1478","1460–Male":"1460–Surnud","1449–Female":"1449–Surnud","1405–1474":"1405–1474","1424–Female":"1424–Surnud","12 August 1474":"12. august 1474","1424":"1424","1478":"1478","1474":"1474","01 Sep 1478":"1. september 1478","1440":"1440","1460":"1460","about 1440":"umbes 1440","about 1460":"umbes 1460","1405":"1405","1449":"1449","Poltimore, Devon, England":"Poltimore, Devon, England"},"fi":{"about 1440–01 Sep 1478":"noin 1440–1. syyskuuta 1478","1440–1478":"1440–1478","1460–Male":"1460–Kuollut","1449–Female":"1449–Kuollut","1405–1474":"1405–1474","1424–Female":"1424–Kuollut","12 August 1474":"12. elokuuta 1474","1424":"1424","1478":"1478","1474":"1474","01 Sep 1478":"1. syyskuuta 1478","1440":"1440","1460":"1460","about 1440":"noin 1440","about 1460":"noin 1460","1405":"1405","1449":"1449","Poltimore, Devon, England":"Poltimore, Devon, England"},"fr":{"about 1440–01 Sep 1478":"environ 1440–1 septembre 1478","1440–1478":"1440–1478","1460–Male":"1460–Décédé","1449–Female":"1449–Décédée","1405–1474":"1405–1474","1424–Female":"1424–Décédée","12 August 1474":"12 août 1474","1424":"1424","1478":"1478","1474":"1474","01 Sep 1478":"1 septembre 1478","1440":"1440","1460":"1460","about 1440":"environ 1440","about 1460":"environ 1460","1405":"1405","1449":"1449","Poltimore, Devon, England":"Poltimore, Devon, Angleterre","lifeS